claims:
1. A method of treatment of a subject in need thereof, comprising at least one of:
A) treating a subject suffering from a granuloma comprising administering a composition comprising an effective amount of Thymosin beta 4 (Tβ4), a Tβ4 isoform, oxidized Tβ4, Thymosin β4 sulfoxide, a polypeptide or any other actin sequestering or bundling proteins having an actin binding domain, or a peptide fragment comprising amino acid sequence LKKTET or conservative variants thereof and a pharmaceutically acceptable carrier to the subject;
